<br>
Another spot is IGs at Permafrost, you can get exp there if you're low-mid 50s (I think, I haven't camped them so I don't know what level they are)<br>
<br>
On the other hand, I prefer to farm unused low level dungeons where FS drops, like SolA.  It's especially nice when there's a vendor in the zone to sell all the FS to.<br>
<br>
I don't know of any good cash spots in Kunark or Luclin though.  Velious has Crystal Caverns, which can be an OK farm spot if you have some way to use the dwarves as vendors.  I haven't farmed there for cash, but I have for crystal silks.<br>
<br>
I've been doing Droga recently for the Chardok quests, and I can tell ya, it's a pretty crappy place for farming cash.  At least I've had a lot lower cashflow there than otherwhere.<br>
<br>
Luclin I just haven't explored the lower level zones as much yet, been busy getting AXP in the upper level ones. <p><a href="http://fu-profiles.vestergren.nu/view_player.php?uid=118">Danariel Draconian</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucaeadyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>caeadyen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#333333>(1/19/02 5:50:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=85.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to get lots of Platinum as a mage</span><hr size=1> It's not an uber way to get cash but this method isn't bad either  (I can get hundreds of pp this way an hour or two).<br>
<br>
In OOT there is an island with a spawn of 4 spectres on a 5 minute timer.  Be sure you can pull singles.  At lvl 55 I could pull a single but if I didn't bring the spec to the edge of the island my pet pet jumped in and aggroed all the other specs which wasn't good.<br>
<br>
Specs can drop anything from 0 to 5pp each and either one of three types of scythes.  The best one sells for 12pp.<br>
<br>
While medding or waiting for respawn, there are skellies and gargoyles.  Skellies are phs for gargoyles.  I've seen gargoyles drop 2 eyes at a time once but sometimes none.  Those sell for about 8pp.<br>
<br>
Won't get any exp but it's something different while taking a break from questing or the usual exp grind.<br>
<br>
